  "outcome": "A B2C notifier builds a complete CHED-PP draft (DRAFT.GB.2026.1525765) from the dashboard through commodity code search (06011010, 06042090), bulk commodity details, consignment details, transport/BCP, goods movement services and contacts, then on the Documents page selects a Phytosanitary certificate and attempts to attach a .txt file, and the separate upload service rejects it with the error-summary alert 'The selected file must be a DOC, JPEG, PDF, PNG or XLS'.",
